    header.header
      h1.header__title 
        a(href="#") Climate Mind
      .header__menu
        ul.menu
          li.menu__item
            a(href="#about").menu__item-link About
          li.menu__item
            a(href="#team").menu__item-link Team
          li.menu__item
            a(href="#get-involved").menu__item-link Get Involved
          
    .hero
      .hero__content
        .hero__slogan Powering climate conversations.
        img.hero__image(src="images/logos/climateMind-world.svg")
      
    .teaser
      .teaser__wrapper
        h2.teaser__headline Why do we need Climate Mind?
        .teaser__content
          .teaser__text It can be a real challenge to communicate the realities of climate change to people around you, especially those who have different values and personal interests. 
          .teaser__text Often, people don’t realize actionable solutions already exist that don’t require an overhaul of their personality or beliefs.
        .teaser__subline Our aim is to make conversations about climate change easier.
      .teaser__decoration
        .teaser__wave-top
        .teaser__wave-bottom

    .about-us#about
      h2.about-us__headline What is Climate Mind?
      .about-us__wrapper

        .about-us__content
          .about-us__subline A tool to relate everyone and their lives to the effects of climate change.
          .about-us__text We are creating a web app that helps users explore how their values and personal interests are vulnerable to the effects of climate change.
          .about-us__text We aim to inspire users to take action with a range of attractive solutions consistent with their values that they can get excited about.
          .about-us__text We are in the early stages of development and are welcoming new people to the team.

        .about-us__teaser
          img.about-us__icon(src="images/what-is-climateMind.svg")
          .about-us__slogan Open up constructive conversations about the impact of climate change.
            
    .insights
      h2.insights__headline How will it work?
      .insights__wrapper
        .insights__content
          .insights__subline Climate Mind consists of a web application and a knowledge base.
          .insights__text The finished product will guide users through the process of personalizing climate conversations with others and responding to common climate change myths. Then it will provide achievable action proposals that align with the values and interests of the user.
          .insights__text The knowledge base will collect knowledge available on climate change and interpret it as sets of concepts and the relationships between them.

